{"title":"大地","authors":["黄咏梅"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄咏梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵风传来的话题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你粗犷博大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你井然而狂奔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我都一样爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你岂只给了我立足之处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给了血脉与魂啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你是土黄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以我也以黄得如一抔泥土为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你是沸腾的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以我也沸腾得如一条巨龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你是文明之源"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以我对你如此忠诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一些华丽的诗语向我飘来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煽动我唾弃你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我始终如一地爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果不爱你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那岂不是不爱自已的血脉与灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魂？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}